OL,3,CNetwork Rail warns people are 'risking
OL,4,Cit all' at level crossings
OL,6,FWatch: CCTV released by Network Rail
OL,7,Fshows a number of near misses on the
OL,8,Frailway network.
OL,10,FNetwork Rail has warned that people
OL,11,Fare 'risking it all' when using level
OL,12,Fcrossings on the railway network.
OL,14,FThe company, which is responsible for
OL,15,Fmaintaining tracks and infrastructure,
OL,16,Fsays there have been more than 1500
OL,17,Fincidents in the past four years.
OL,19,FIt says distractions, such as mobile
OL,20,Fphone usage, is driving a rise in near
OL,21,Fmiss incidents, which are up by 16%.
