OL,3,CNetwork Rail warns people are 'risking
OL,4,Cit all' at level crossings
OL,6,FIt is urging people to be careful when
OL,7,Fon the railway, and to be fully alert
OL,8,Fwhen using crossings.
OL,10,FThe release of the footage comes as
OL,11,Fnew research commissioned by Network
OL,12,FRail shows that 47% of people in the
OL,13,FSouth East admit they have made a
OL,14,Fmistake whilst being distracted by
OL,15,Ftheir phone.
OL,17,FThe data also shows that young people
OL,18,Fare among the most distracted, with
OL,19,F87% of Gen Z and 70% of Millennials
OL,20,Fadmitting to mistakes.
