OL,6,F35% of people in the South East also
OL,7,Fadmitted they pay more attention
OL,8,Fwhilst crossing a road, compared to
OL,9,Fusing a level crossing on the railway.
OL,11,FIncidents on level crossings can be
OL,12,Ffatal or life changing. Lucy Ruck was
OL,13,Fonly 17 when she lost her leg in a
OL,14,Frailway incident at Farnborough North
OL,15,Flevel crossing.
